:

1. *Kaznu* je dobio zbog prekoračenja brzine. (He was punished for speeding.)
2. Sudija je izrekao *kaznu*. (The judge pronounced the penalty.)
3. On je tražio da mu se smanji *kazna*. (He asked for his penalty to be reduced.)
4. On nije mogao da plati *kaznu*. (He couldn't pay the fine.)
5. *Kazne* su uvećane za prekršaje. (Fines have been increased for offenses.)